ApplcoreAttrValException

public ApplcoreAttrValException(java.lang.String pErrorCode,
                                java.lang.String pEODefName,
                                java.lang.String pEOAttrName,
                                java.lang.Object pEOAttrVal,
                                java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object> msgTokens)
Raise an AttrValException with tokens. The message dictionary resource bundle is used, and tokens re-formatted to match.

Parameters:
pErrorCode - A message dictionary message, in the format application:::message Example: FND:::MY_TEST_MESSAGE
pEODefName - The EO where this error occurred.
pEOAttrName - The attribute where this error occurred.
pEOAttrVal - The attribute value
msgTokens - A map of tokens to substitute. This is expected to be a Map with token name as the key, and an object of appropriate type for the token data type as the value.
